  <!-- ══ PANEL: COUNTRIES ══ -->
  <div class="panel visible" id="countriesSection">
    <div class="section-card">
      <div class="section-body">
        <div class="instruction">
          👉 Click each flag. Say the country name out loud, then say: "I'm from ___".
        </div>

        <div class="country-grid" id="countryGrid">
          <div class="country-card" onclick="toggleCard(this)"><div class="flag"><svg viewBox="0 0 60 40" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="60" height="40" fill="#c1272d"/><polygon points="30,9 33.5,17 42,17 35,22.5 37.5,31 30,26 22.5,31 25,22.5 18,17 26.5,17" fill="none" stroke="#006233" stroke-width="2"/></svg></div><div class="name">Morocco</div></div>
